---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 39
  - Title: Purgatorio
    Chapter:
      - XXVIII
      - Verse: 91
By: Dante
Tags:
  - Creation=The World Begins in Perfection
---
The highest Good, who himself alone doth please, made man good and for
goodness, and gave this place to him as an earnest of eternal peace.
